{"tid":424000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"点解要去香港买奶粉先安心？原因终于揭开...","createTime":"2017-10-04T10:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T09:03:26.000Z","uid":148865,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfcb5d3fc552c1169c49578e2c15ffba432b32a","tid":424000,"uid":148865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"好多妈妈钟意去香港购买奶粉<br />\n搵人代购都要买香港嘅奶粉<br />\n因为觉得安全放心<br />\n<br />\n但点解香港奶粉会特别令人安心？<br />\n系因为...<br />\n01<br />\n安全标准高<br />\n香港奶粉&quot;准入门槛&quot;较高，香港地区执行嘅系国际通行嘅CODEX标准，系被世界各国公认嘅国际食品标准。从各个方面对配方奶粉嘅质量作出严格规定。<br />\n<br />\n02<br />\n港版确实100%原装进口<br />\n香港无奶源生产基地同奶粉加工厂，所以港版国外品牌奶粉称得上系&ldquo;纯正百分百金口&rdquo;，直接原装进口，无经过其他分装。<br />\n<br />\n03<br />\n价格相对便宜<br />\n香港好多进口商品系免税或者低税率，仲有人民币兑港币汇率影响，所以好多妈妈选择系香港选购奶粉，实惠又安心。<br />\n香港奶粉令人安心<br />\n连续14年全港销量NO.1嘅香港美赞臣<br />\n更加令人安心！"},{"pid":"dfb0442628a7d13d8f4d7fa5f1a6dff4eac97183","tid":424000,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06db8fd31266e30be716863d9392c52567fc937","tid":424000,"uid":148865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3639340af65fb089012c3bf5d8b21c5afb11604","tid":424000,"uid":148865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90a7d6273a0fec1baa8e14e0c4d978d14332c0","tid":424000,"uid":131686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"內容農場標題同殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1ec2725c7afe602d0a0cefa42abbfccf0b6e80","tid":424000,"uid":148865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite